   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Thatres, daughter of Sokmenis, her mother being Aphrodisia, with her guardian, her husband Socrates, Antinoite, and however else he is styled, has received an allotment of the property belonging to us, sharing jointly and equally in the portion which has fallen to me...</ab>
